itunes:title: If You Have Anxiety About What You Want To Do In Life & The Future
title: If You Have Anxiety About What You Want To Do In Life & The Future
itunes:author: Joey Kidney
itunes:subtitle: What's Next?
itunes:summary:
Our future is a very scary thing which is really sad because it is what we live for, so we need to stop looking at it so negatively and start to see the positives. I invited my girlfriend Angelica on the podcast today to talk about her journey. Because just like mine is has taken many twists and turns in directions that weren't planned.. and that's ok!
